Imports: cli, grid (>= 4.1.0), gtable, lifecycle, rlang (>= 1.2.0), S7,
        scales (>= 1.1.1), vctrs (>= 0.6.0)
Suggests: knitr, ragg, rmarkdown, svglite, testthat (>= 3.0.0), vdiffr,
        withr
